column5: Easy drilling this year eh?  Thanks for the recap, I can't get over the average size of the fish I'm seeing!
Some nice Lakers  were caught on a few of your outings thanks for sharing.
Great video. The ice at the beginning looked paper thin. It definitely was a warm winter for any ice. Pulled in some good size fish in that video.
great video.. Ice looked to thin for me LOL
Nice going Steve. I didnt get a laker this year as I stayed away from that so called UNSAFE  ice.LOL I,ll take whities everyday though.  Great vid.
